text: Hi Harry. I must apologise as I haven't fed back to you, I didn't get the notification of your message. I've adjusted the settings, so hopefully it won't happen again. I'll check back here regularly from now on just in case.

Are you still working on the shot? From what I saw it was a really positive start. I noticed some pixel stretching bottom of the frame and a matte edge travelling up his shoulder. The lighting is not quite right yet.  Please share your latest as I'm sure you've adjusted it in the last month.
